lead_paragraph: Bournemouth striker Callum Wilson pounced in the closing stages of a tight tussle with West Bromwich Albion to give the home side a 1-0 win on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Wilson Gets Bournemouth Going With 1-0 Win Over West Brom
